These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
There are 2 different favourite colors: ebony, aquamarine
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, subway
1. the person driving the van is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| Color         | aquamarine   | ebony |
| Transport   | van  | subway      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, dannemann
2 different pets are kept: cat, dog
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
3. the software-developer is not to the right of the librarian##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the owner of the dog##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Cigar    | cain        | dannemann    |
| Pet       | cat         | dog |
| Job         | software-developer | librarian   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different games are played: bridge, canasta
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
House: victorian, townhouse
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
2. the townhouse house is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Game   | bridge       | canasta |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| House   | victorian | townhouse |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

